name: コンビニ店員
text:
17円のお返しです
ありがとうございましたー
trans: Your change is 17 yen. Thank you and have a nice day!

name: 透
trans: Wait, were you there the whole time?

name: 円香
text: 入った時から、いるのは気付いてたけど
trans: But I noticed you when I came in.

name: コンビニ店員
trans: ...one item for 238 yen, one for 157 yen.

name: 円香
text: あ……あと、カフェラテのMで
trans: Oh, and a cafe latte, medium please.

name: コンビニ店員
text:
カフェラテMですねー……
──合計３点、545円になります
trans:
One medium-size cafe latte...
──Your total comes to 545 yen.

name: 円香
text:
ICカードでお願いします
……じゃ、お疲れ
trans:
I'll pay by IC card.
...See you.

name: コンビニ店員
text: ありがとうございましたー
trans: Thank you, have a nice day.

name: 透
text: あー……コーヒー飲んでた

name: 円香
trans: What's got into you? It's night.

name: 透
text: 夜でもおはようなんだって
trans: Even when it's night, it's "good morning", they said.

name: 円香
text:
働き方が色々だから、
時間帯問わずでおはよう……なんだっけ
trans: Everyone's working hours are different, so greet them with "good morning" no matter what time it is... or something like that?

name: 円香
trans: You've been doing all sorts of stuff, huh?

name: 透
text:
え、うん
テレビ局行ったよ、挨拶
trans:
Eh? Yeah.
I went to a TV station, met people.

name: 円香
text: なんか嫌。勘違いしてるみたいで
trans: I just don't like them. Makes me look like I'm putting on airs.

name: 円香
text:
っていうかさ、
浅倉は、なんで──……
trans: Seriously though, Asakura, why did you──...

name: 透
text: おはようございました

name: 円香
text: ふっ……それ、絶対違うでしょ
trans: Heh... I'm pretty sure they don't say that.
